# Weather Application - Setup and other info

## FIRST TIME DO THIS
- navigate to client folder
- *npm install*

## Running the Weather App

### Server
- Open new terminal
- Navigate to the /server folder
- *node index.js*

### Client
- Open new terminal
- Navigate to /client folder
- *npm run dev*

---
    View client here: http://localhost:5173/
---


NOTICE: Weather graph resets at 2am, but all data is still stored in the db
